          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唐武则天时，薛刚闯祸，满门抄斩。薛刚逃出，占据寒山，积粮招兵，为报复之计。时薛刚兄薛猛，被武三"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "思全家诛戮。有儿薛蛟，尚在襁褓，亦将受戮。薛猛有至友徐策，服官在朝。闻信后，往法场祭之，暗将己"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿藏之金斗，换出薛蛟，以留薛门后裔。行刑时徐策子被狂风吹去。迨薛蛟年长，臂力过人，徐策亦拜相。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一日徐策往朝堂，薛蛟与书童至门外，将石狮举起戏玩。适徐策回府，见狮易处，问书童，知薛蛟所为，乃"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唤薛蛟入祖先堂，观薛家被难图。薛蛟莫明其故。徐策为细讲当日冤情，声明薛蛟并非亲生子，实薛门后裔。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "薛蛟闻言大哭，誓必报仇。徐策乃修书付薛蛟，嘱至寒山助叔报仇。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "注释"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "剧中白口至“家院磨墨伺候”，接唱一段，全神贯注疾徐高下，最难得中。前往春桂，听到刘鸿声唱，最为"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "出色。其后《跑城》，乃徐策子回来，做工首推三麻子。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "根据《戏考》第一册整理"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（书童上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "书童",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "书童书童，气概威风。人人怕我，"
        },
        {
          "character": "书童",
          "line_type": "笑",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哈哈！"
        },
        {
          "character": "书童",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我还怕相公。"
        },
        {
          "character": "书童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咱家相府书童便是，今日相爷不在府中，不免请相公出来，同到府前玩耍玩耍，\n岂不是好。\n有请相公。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（薛蛟上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛蛟",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "忽听书童来相请，\n快步如梭到前厅。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛蛟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "书童，请我出堂何事？"
        },
        {
          "character": "书童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "相公。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛蛟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唔。"
        },
        {
          "character": "书童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今日相爷不在府中，我们到府门外玩耍玩耍可好？"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛蛟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如此带路。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛蛟",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "豪杰开言笑开怀，\n不觉来到府门外。"
        },
        {
          "character": "书童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "相公。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛蛟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "做什么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "书童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你看这一对玉石狮子，哪一个举得起它，就是个状元。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛蛟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哪个先举？"
        },
        {
          "character": "书童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "若论年纪，就该书童先举。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛蛟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "就让你先举。"
        },
        {
          "character": "书童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "慢些，待我把这些余气吐完了，洒洒架子。哎呀，这狮子好像生了根一般，你\n来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛蛟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你且让开。"
        },
        {
          "character": "书童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "下边听着，府门外有玉狮一对，有人高高举起，低低放下，万官能做，万马能\n骑。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛蛟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来也。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛蛟",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "向前来举起石狮子，\n双手轮舞显奇能。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（内开道声。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "书童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "快放下。相爷回府，完了完了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（薛蛟下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "书童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，两个狮子，放在一堆了真真淘气。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（书童下。家院引徐策同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐策",
          "line_type": "笑",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呵呵呵。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐策",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "朝罢归相府，名高镇帝邦。又只见玉狮子，搬在一旁。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐策",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓。府门外狮子为何蹲在一处？这就奇了。\n来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "家院",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐策",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "传书童。"
        },
        {
          "character": "家院",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "相爷传书童。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（书童上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "书童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来了。相爷在上，书童叩头。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐策",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我且问你，府门外有何人到过？相公可曾出府？"
        },
        {
          "character": "书童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "没有人到此处，相公也没有。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐策",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "府门外石狮子，为何搬在一处？"
        },
        {
          "character": "书童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这，这个……"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐策",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "讲。"
        },
        {
          "character": "书童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不瞒你老人家，这是小人搬在一处的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐策",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "噢，是你。"
        },
        {
          "character": "书童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不敢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐策",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "依然分为两处。"
        },
        {
          "character": "书童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这事极容易。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（书童分。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "书童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启相爷：今日力气用尽了，明日分开罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐策",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "胡说，请相公出来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "书童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。\n有请相公。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（薛蛟上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛蛟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "书童，做什么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "书童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "相爷唤你。他若问你可曾出府，你只说没有。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛蛟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。\n爹爹在上，孩儿拜揖。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐策",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "罢了，儿吓，为父的上朝，你可曾到府外玩耍么？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（书童做手势。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐策",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唔，你在此做什么。"
        },
        {
          "character": "书童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小人一时发了鸡爪疯。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐策",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唔，还不退下。"
        },
        {
          "character": "书童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（书童下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐策",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿吓，府门外石狮子为何搬在一处，是何人搬的？"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛蛟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启禀爹爹：孩儿与书童，在府门外玩耍，见爹爹未曾回府，是孩儿搬在一处。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐策",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为父的不信，你可依然分开。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛蛟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孩儿借道。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛蛟",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "爹爹在上传下令，\n豪杰一时胆气生。\n放下两边见分明。"
        },
        {
          "character": "用力举起石狮子、徐策",
          "line_type": "笑",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哈哈哈！"
        },
        {
          "character": "用力举起石狮子、徐策",
          "line_type": "二黄散板",
          "musical_style": "二黄散板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "这才是父是英雄儿好汉，\n强将手下无弱兵。"
        },
        {
          "character": "用力举起石狮子、徐策",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿吓，随父到祖先堂上。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛蛟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（徐策、薛蛟同走圆场。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐策",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿吓，拜过祖先。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛蛟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。爹爹，祖先堂上，为何挂这幅图画，是何道理？"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐策",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿吓，这不是我家祖先，乃是薛家的祖先。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛蛟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "薛家的祖先，为何挂在我家堂上。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐策",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只因他全家被奸党所害，做了刀头之鬼，故此为父不忍，悬挂家中。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛蛟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "爹爹，那上面白袍将军，他是何人？"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐策",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他乃唐朝有功之臣，名唤薛仁贵，跨海征东，有十大功劳，圣上封他为平辽王\n之职。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛蛟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "爹爹，那黑汉是谁？"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐策",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你再也不要提起他来。他乃薛丁山之子，名唤薛刚，只因圣上大放花灯，他酒\n醉出府，闯下泼天大祸，打死太子，惊崩圣驾，奸臣张天佐，与他世代结仇，\n一本默奏上殿，可怜他满门诛戮。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛蛟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎，可惨吓可惨。爹爹下面有一小小孩童，他是何人？"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐策",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他乃薛猛之子，名叫薛蛟。周岁未满，也在法场受刑。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛蛟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这等说，岂不是连根都除了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐策",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此子还未曾死。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛蛟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为怎么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐策",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "朝中有一契友，心中不忍，他将自己亲生儿子去到法场换了出来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛蛟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "爹爹，此子有多大年纪了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐策",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此子么，也有儿般长，儿般大。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛蛟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这等说，此子无志。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐策",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎见得无志？"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛蛟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有这大年纪，怎么不去报仇？"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐策",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳，唗！你自己海深冤仇，不能报得，反说别人么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛蛟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我家有甚冤仇？"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐策",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为父的吃了几杯闷酒，说话之间，有些前言不对后语，改日说罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（薛蛟跪，哭。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛蛟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，爹爹吓，我家有海深冤仇，望爹爹与孩儿说明。如若不然，孩儿就死尘\n埃。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐策",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我儿吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐策",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "孩儿不必泪双流，\n细听为父说从头：\n是你高祖名仁贵，跨海征东把兵投。\n并肩一字封王侯。\n乃是你二世宗祖亲。\n圣上亲封西辽王。\n张天佐与薛家世代结冤仇。\n奸贼上殿奏一本。\n可怜他满门受非刑。\n也在法场丧残生。\n换出我儿后代根。\n乃是薛家后代根。"
        },
        {
          "character": "那白袍将军非是别一个、圣上见他功劳大、这一位名唤薛丁山、征西有功于朝廷、只因你三叔闯下祸、你父阳和为总督、我舍自己亲生子、蛟儿非是徐门后、薛蛟",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "听说不是徐门后，\n唬得我魂不在身。\n不报冤仇誓不休！"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐策",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哈哈哈，儿吓，你要报仇，倒也不难。你有一婶娘，现在卧龙山，招兵买马，\n积草囤粮，你且在后堂饱餐，待为父修书一封，与你前去，发兵报仇便了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛蛟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孩儿知道。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（薛蛟下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐策",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "家院磨墨伺候。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐策",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "墨浓笔饱诉衷肠，\n止不住双泪涌胸膛。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（徐策写。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐策",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "拜上多拜上，\n拜上卧龙纪鸾英：\n薛猛之子名薛蛟。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（薛蛟上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐策",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿吓，"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐策",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "一路行去要当心。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛蛟",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "向前来拜别我的父，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（薛蛟哭。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛蛟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎，爹爹吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛蛟",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "一心打马往前行。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐策",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿吓，回来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛蛟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "爹爹何事？"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐策",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你今前去卧龙山婶娘那里，搬兵报仇，报仇之后，回来我若还在世，亲眼看见，\n也不枉为父一片热心。我若不在，你可手拿几张纸钱，走到为父坟前，大哭\n一场，多拜几拜，儿吓，难道为父当真受了你的不成，也等那旁人叹息几句。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（徐策哭。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐策",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吾儿吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛蛟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，爹爹这等说，孩儿不去了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐策",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你怎的不去？"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛蛟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待爹爹百年以后再去。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（徐策笑。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐策",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿吓，为父的还不老，你只管前去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛蛟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孩儿不去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐策",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唔，你再说不去，我就打。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛蛟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "打死孩儿也不去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐策",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好没来由。吓，若是我的亲生金斗孩儿，叫他往东，他就在东，叫他往西，他\n就在西。吓，这等看起来，好不气死我也。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛蛟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "爹爹不必如此，孩儿愿去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐策",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你是怎讲？"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛蛟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孩儿愿去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐策",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哈哈哈，好吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛蛟",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "拜别爹爹上了马，"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛蛟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，爹吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛蛟",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "去到卧龙把兵搬。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐策",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "徐蛟儿吓。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛蛟",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "小豪杰打马上阳关，\n要把冤仇一旦伸！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（薛蛟下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐策",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿吓，你真去了！哎，我的儿吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（徐策哭。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐策",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "一见蛟儿去登程，"
        }
      ],
